      "blocks": {
        "p_1": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>when people first used a stick to draw on the ground.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_2": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The link between stationery and people began. The link, time and again, has continued to evolve along with the evolution of people, and continues to exist today.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_3": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>However, its intended purpose has never changed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_4": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We are now rethinking this evolution. Eliminating unnecessary ornamentation and function, we are taking a new look at what’s really necessary, rediscovering essential elements and aiming to finally arrive at what should have existed all along.</p>"
          }
        },
        "p_5": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Stationery, standard & technology.</p>"
          }
        },
